# OData entity set — server-side query composition over the deal book.

@host = http://localhost:8080
@user = u-jokafor

### First page
GET {{host}}/odata/Deals?$top=5
X-User-Id: {{user}}

### Filter by fund with total count
GET {{host}}/odata/Deals?$filter=fundId eq 'fund-iii'&$count=true
X-User-Id: {{user}}

### Watch-list deals, largest exposure first
GET {{host}}/odata/Deals?$filter=status eq 'Watch'&$orderby=outstanding desc
X-User-Id: {{user}}

### Projection
GET {{host}}/odata/Deals?$select=id,name,borrower,netIrrPct&$orderby=netIrrPct desc&$top=5
X-User-Id: {{user}}

### Metadata document
GET {{host}}/odata/$metadata
X-User-Id: {{user}}
